-- Financial Investors Looking at Insolvent Inventux, Berliner Says
-- B y   J u l i e   C r u z
-- 2012-05-22T23:00:00Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-22/financial-investors-looking-at-insolvent-inventux-berliner-says.html
The insolvent German solar company
Inventux Solar Technologies AG is attracting interest from
financial investors,  Berliner Zeitung  reported, citing
insolvency administrator Rolf Rattunde.  Talks with potential investors started several weeks ago,
the newspaper said. Those interested in the Berlin-based company
include financial investors from abroad, according to Berliner
Zeitung.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Julie Cruz in Frankfurt at 
